###  https://w3id.org/mqto/example#AdjustMeltTemp
<https://w3id.org/mqto/example#AdjustMeltTemp> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                        <https://w3id.org/mqto#Countermeasure> ;
                                               <http://rds.posccaesar.org/ontology/lis14/rdl/hasParticipant> <https://w3id.org/mqto/example#DieCastingCell> ;
                                               rdfs:label "Adjust melt holding temperature to alloy specification"@en ;
                                               <https://w3id.org/mqto#hasStepList> <https://w3id.org/mqto/example#AdjustMeltTemp_List1> ;
                                               <https://w3id.org/mqto#mitigates> <https://w3id.org/mqto/example#MeltTempTooHigh> ,
                                                                                 <https://w3id.org/mqto/example#Porosity> ;
                                               <https://w3id.org/mqto#weight> 90 .


